block land-intro
  h3 # d|Bootcamp Taipei is ...
  p Hands-on courses which give journalists the basis of data journalism by experts from all over the world.
  br
  p: b Do you want to play with data?
  p In the age of open data, we need new skills to deal with the overwhelming informations. Data bootcamp Taipei focuses on providing journalists a series of crash courses which guide them to do data journalism from scratch. 
  p With the help of professional lecturers and teaching assistants, you will learn how to do data journalism - getting and scraping data, tools to deal with data, fundamental of data visualization and the most important - actually building a project with people from different domains  - join in the following 2 days g0v hackathon event to bring your idea to life!

  h3 Is Coding Skill a Requirement ?
  p Absolutely #[b Not]! Data Bootcamp Taipei is designed for every journalists regardless of coding skill. So don't worry, you don't have to be a coder to join this workshop.
  p: b ** note: attendees must bring their own laptop and install modern browsers like Chrome or Firefox beforehand.

  //-
    h4 國際視野
    p 來自世界銀行、南華早報、數據中文網等世界各地與台灣相關領域的講者，為各位帶來國際資料新聞的最新現況，和編輯台裡面實際的運作狀況。
    h4 實作訓練
    p 由國內相關領域的專家帶領大家學習與實作。資料新聞課程切分為四大主軸，從案例、資料取得與整理、到資料視覺化，著重在立即上手，確保學習到的技術，能立即應用於新聞報導中。
    h4 參與提案
    p 資料新聞需要的是團隊合作。資料新聞實戰營包含零時政府黑客松的介紹，鼓勵所有參與者接續後兩天的零時政府黑客松提案活動，將創意、報導與技術、社群的力量結合，激發出前所未有的媒體型態與新聞報導。
    h3 #「在這個課程中,我將學會 ...」
    p 如何製作資料新聞、如何取得與爬梳資料、熟悉製作資料新聞的基礎工具、理解資料視覺化的基礎心法，以及最重要的，與跨界成員、組隊打怪的機會與經驗。
    p ** 學員需自備筆記型電腦，並預先安裝 Chrome 及 Firefox 瀏覽器

